修改后：torch_command = os.environ.get(&#39;TORCH_COMMAND&#39;, &#34;pip install torch==1.13.1 torchvision==0.14.1&#34;) &lt;span aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;line-numbers-rows&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;



&lt;pre class=&#34;line-numbers language-javascript&#34; data-language=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34;&gt;ln &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;s &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;usr&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;local&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;bin&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;python3 &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;usr&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;bin&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;python
ln &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;s &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;usr&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;local&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;bin&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;pip3 &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;usr&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;bin&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;pip
&lt;span class=&#34;token literal-property property&#34;&gt;https&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;github&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;com&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token constant&#34;&gt;AUTOMATIC1111&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;stable&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;diffusion&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;webui&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;git
&lt;span class=&#34;token constant&#34;&gt;COMMANDLINE_ARGS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;skip&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;torch&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;cuda&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;test &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;precision full &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;no&lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;half &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;lowvram&lt;span aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; class=&#34;line-numbers-rows&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;weibu.py中将shared.demo.launch()第一行&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;改为share=True&lt;/p&gt;
